 And you really do not want to write 15 lines of code.

00:34:43.640 --> 00:34:47.040
 That's unnecessary repetition, unnecessary cutting and

00:34:47.040 --> 00:34:51.040
 pasting and changing code, if you can keep it really simple.

00:34:51.040 --> 00:34:55.720
 So I can basically build a full set of CRUD forms and

